rn_creature_lvl3.description:
{Tracker}

The Trackers are a collective of humans and elves who have chosen to forge their own path, breaking away from the confines of their respective empires. They have dedicated themselves to the protection of the forests and the service of Mother Nature, aligning themselves with a cause that stands in stark contrast to the profit-driven agendas of the capitalist empires.

